2nd row<p>Ten thousand years ago, Muyun's fairy King was secretly accounted for by holding a Zhuxian figure, and after a long sleep, he awakened in the famous "Muyun waste" of the southern Yun Empire in the Land of Heaven. When Muyun first woke up, he was deliberately bothered by the student Miaoxianyu. Muyun easily completed the Miaoxianyu trap, and he gave more and more alchemy skills by analogy, so the Alchemy masters outside the door could not ask for appreciation.
